:if:<register.exists(insightfulblue)>=false
    @text.show(Who are you?~My name's Blue.~I was once the~Kanto Champion.*Although it was~short-lived thanks~to Red...*Anyway, take a good~look around you...*A volcano erupts,~and just like that,~a whole town disappears.~We can go on winning~and losing in Pok√©mon,~but if nature so~much as twitches,~we can be overwhelmed~in a second...~That's the way it is...~But, anyway,~I'm still a Trainer.~If I see a strong~opponent, it makes me want~to battle.)
